//- ============================== Mixins
include ../../../../_pug/_mixin
// ============================== templateContainer
header(class="template-header" ng-controller="CtrlHeader" ng-include="'../ngMaster/header.php'")
|
|
section(class="template-wrapper" )
    aside(class="template-asideLeft o-aside-Item" ng-init="s_actividad = 1; DragandDrop()")
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction" data-activities-count="1" ng-click="s_actividad = 1" ng-class="(s_actividad == 1) ? 'is-active' : '';")
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction" data-activities-count="2" ng-click="s_actividad = 2" ng-class="(s_actividad == 2) ? 'is-active' : '';")

    |
    |
    
    div(class="template-section m-a" ng-init="DragandDrop()")
        section(class="template-content u-animationFadeDown" ng-show="s_actividad == 1")
            h5 #[strong.u-textColor_4 1. ] Read the following examples. Pay attention to the verbs in bold:
            div(class="row mt50 flex align-items-center")
                div(class="col xs10 md6 col-center")
                    .c-cardBlue
                        div(class="c-cardBlueContent")
                            p.mb20The The company #[strong was shipping] the apples by boat. #[br] The apples #[strong were being shipped] by boat. 
                            p.mb20The A #[i farmer ] #[strong picked] the apples first, then he #[strong cleaned] them, and finally, he #[strong packed] and #[strong shipped] them to the market.
                            p.mb20The First the #[i apples ] #[strong were picked], then they #[strong were cleaned], and finally, they #[strong were packed] and #[strong shipped] to the market.
                            

                div(class="col xs12 md4")
                    img(src="unit_1/module_4/assets/images/act_7_1.png", alt="" class="u-responsive-img")



        section(class="template-content u-animationFadeDown" ng-show="s_actividad == 2")

            div(class="row-flex mt50-xs mt50-md mt10-sm")
                div(class="col-flex-xs12 col-flex-md8 offset-md2 col-center mt10-sm mt30-md")
                    div(class="row-flex")
                        h5 #[strong.u-textColor_4 2. ] Complete the examples below with the verbs in the box. 
                        h6.ml20 Drag and drop the verbs' box into the right phrase.
                div(class="row mt30")
                    div(class="row ")
                        div(class="row-flex justify-around")
                            div(class="dragCont ml10")
                                div(class="drag padding5") was given
                            div(class="dragCont ml10")
                                div(class="drag padding5") were being chased
                            div(class="dragCont ml10")
                                div(class="drag padding5") was considered
                            div(class="dragCont ml10")
                                div(class="drag padding5") was being repaired
                div(class="col-flex-xs12 col-flex-md8 offset-md2 col-center mt10-sm mt30-md")
 
                        
                div(class="row mt20 flex align-items-center")
                    div(class="col xs12 md4 showTo-md")
                        img(src="unit_1/module_4/assets/images/act_7a.png", alt="" class="u-responsive-img")
                    div(class="col xs12 md8")
                        h5 The passive voice is used when:
                        div(class="row")
                            p(class="mt20 mb20"): h6(class="u-textColor_4") • We do not know who did the action:
                            p(class="u-textColor_4 mt40")
                                span(class="u-textColor_1-dark") This book
                                    span(class="drop ancho220 h30")
                                    | to her for Christmas.
                            p(class="u-textColor_4")
                                span(class="u-textColor_1-dark") Before discovering the cure, that illness 
                                    span(class="drop ancho220 h30")
                                    | lethal.
                            p(class="mt40 mb20"): h6(class="u-textColor_4") • The receiver of the action is more important:
                            p(class="u-textColor_4 mt40")
                                span(class="u-textColor_1-dark") The zebras
                                    span(class="drop ancho220 h30")
                                    | by a couple of lions.
                            p(class="u-textColor_4")
                                span(class="u-textColor_1-dark") The car 
                                    span(class="drop ancho220 h30")
                                    | by our old mechanic.
    |
    |
    aside(class="template-asideRight o-aside-Item") 
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction openNotice is-active u-bgIconAlert" ng-click="idNotice = 2")
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction u-bgIconRefresh" ng-click="reloadDragandDrop()" ng-show="s_actividad == 2")
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction u-bgIconCheck" ng-show="s_actividad == 2")
